roximation for this basic problem. Our algorithm relies on several\nnew ideas of independent interests in signal estimation, including\nhigh-sensitivity frequency estimation and new error analysis with sharper noise\ncontrol.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 2 May 2022 05:15:54 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 15 Nov 2022 02:20:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-16"}
