 who interacted with the agent whose\nutterances were synthesized from spontaneous speech tended to rate their\nconversation with the agent as closer to a human conversation. These results\nsuggest that speech synthesis built on spontaneous speech is essential to\nrealize a conversational agent as a social actor.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 2 May 2022 09:00:35 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 3 May 2022 15:28:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-10-20"}
