mples per second with less than\n10GB of memory on a single GPU. We will release the code in\nhttps://github.com/MCG-NJU/APP-Net.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 2 May 2022 12:21:11 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 18 Aug 2022 15:21:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-08-19"}
